#: ../../asset_management/data_protection.rst:77
#| msgid ""
#| "Hard Disk (HDD) manufacturers keep their statistics to themselves. A "
#| "manufacturer guaranty buys you a new disk, but no data. Google for One "
#| "has done a large scale study on `HDD <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
