msgid ""
"Hard Disk drive (HDD) manufacturers keep their statistics to themselves. A "
"manufacturer's guarantee buys you a new disk, but no data on how long it "
"might last. Backblaze, a storage provider, reported a 1.5% annualized "
"failure rate in 2023 based on an inventory of 237,278 hard drives. Google "
"has done a large-scale study on `HDD <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Hard_disk_drive>`_ failure mechanisms: `Disk Failures study <https://"
"research.google.com/archive/disk_failures.pdf>`_."
msgstr ""
"Els fabricants de discs durs (HDD) guarden les seves estadístiques per a si "
"mateixos. La garantia d'un fabricant us fa comprar un disc nou, però no hi "
"ha dades sobre el temps que pot durar. Backblaze, un proveïdor "
"d'emmagatzematge, va informar d'una taxa de fallada anual de l'1,5% el 2023 "
"basada en un inventari de 237.278 discs durs. Google ha fet un estudi a gran "
"escala sobre els mecanismes de fallada dels `HDD "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hard_disk_drive>`: `Estudi de fallades de "
"disc («Disk Failures study») <https://research.google.com/archive/disk_failure"
"s.pdf>`_."

