#: ../../asset_management/data_protection.rst:209
msgid "Human and Data Loss"
msgstr "Humans i la pèrdua de les dades"

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../asset_management/data_protection.rst:211
#| msgid ""
#| "Human error, as in everything, is a major problem in data loss. Take a "
#| "deep breath and stop. Panic is a common reaction, and people do really "
#| "stupid things. Experienced users will pull the wrong drive from a `RAID "
#| "<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RAID>`_ array or reformat a drive, "
